mknod
    pathname
    mode
        bitwise OR of
            file mode
                mode bits from inode(7)
                    07777 mask
            type of node
                S_IFSOCK
                S_IFREG
                S_IFBLK
                S_IFCHR
                S_IFIFO
        affected by umask
    dev
        for type S_IFCHR or S_IFBLK
            specifies major and minor; see makedev(3)
